                },
                {
                  "kind": "paragraph",
                  "inlines": [
                    {
                      "text": "The animation depicts a pivotal moment in the life of Nathilda Rockeira, a deeply introspective teenager. After a heated argument with her parents about her lack of academic motivation and their concerns for her future, an upset Nathilda flees to her sanctuary – the cemetery. There, she walks solemnly to her hidden radio, presses play on an Evanescence song (her favorite band), and climbs onto a tombstone's steps to sit alone with the music.\n"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
